result.subject: Entire office network down
result.description: An urgent network issue affecting all departments, with all network access down across the entire office. The problem began around 10:30 AM today. As a result, employees are unable to access the internet, file servers, or any internal systems. The number of affected users is approximately 50.

result.subject: CRM software not loading
result.description: The CRM software is not launching for any users. When attempting to open the CRM software, users receive an error message saying "Application Failed to Load." This issue is blocking all sales and customer service activities. This is a high-priority issue as it is affecting 20 users in the Sales department, and it is critical that this is resolved promptly to ensure minimal disruption to business operations. As there are no screenshots available, please contact me at the provided email or phone number during our preferred contact time for further assistance. Your prompt attention to this issue would be greatly appreciated.

result.subject: Printer not responding.
result.description: The printer was working fine yesterday but now shows an error message and produces no prints despite being powered on.

result.subject: Requesting admin access to server
result.description: As a senior developer in the Development department, I need admin access to manage system configurations related to our project. Currently, I only have limited user access, which restricts my ability to make necessary changes. This issue affects only me.

result.subject: Wi-Fi not working in conference room
result.description: The Wi-Fi connection in the conference room is not working. No devices can connect to the network in the conference room, while Wi-Fi works fine in other areas of the office. This issue is affecting 10 users in the Conference Room.

result.subject: Excel crashing when opening large files
result.description: Excel crashes whenever opening files larger than 50MB. This issue has been occurring for the past week and affects multiple users in the finance team. Currently, 7 users are impacted.

result.subject: Missing desk chair
result.description: My desk chair has been missing for a few days from my workstation. I’ve reported it to the office admin team, but it hasn’t been replaced yet. This issue is impacting only me, with 1 user affected, within the Operations department.

result.subject: Slow internet speed in accounting department
result.description: Internet speed has been very slow for the past few days in the accounting department. The internet speed has dropped significantly, and it’s impacting the ability to access cloud-based tools. This issue has been ongoing for about 3 days.

result.subject: Unable to access project repository
result.description: I do not have access to the project repository. I need access to complete my tasks, but I keep getting a permission denied error when I try to access it. This is blocking my work.

result.subject: Keyboard malfunctioning
result.description: The keyboard is not responding to certain keys. Specifically, some keys on my keyboard, including the space bar and 'Enter' key, are not responding. It is making it difficult to work efficiently. This issue affects only one user.
